        {
            "id": 6322798,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 貝克休斯(BKR-US)大漲5.03%，報56.63美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>貝克休斯(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:BKR:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/BKR\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">BKR-US</a>)截至台北時間27日02:56股價上漲2.71美元，報56.63美元，漲幅5.03%，成交量10,397,892（股），盤中最高價56.63美元、最低價54.82美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+0.68%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.67%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+0.66%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：-0.06%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>貝克休斯(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:BKR:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/BKR\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">BKR-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+5.19%</li> <li>近 1 月：+19.16%</li> <li>近 3 月：+14%</li> <li>近 6 月：+17.09%</li> <li>今年以來：+14.38%</li></ul></section></main>",
